name: Iron Sharpens Iron by FightHers V2

metadata.name: Christella Cepeda #1 by Gemma Fleming
metadata.description:
Gemma Flemming is a West Coast transplant Filipina American living in New York. Her career in the creative field has spanned over 16 years of personal and commissioned portraits, editorials, and films.

When not on assignment, her past time is spent competing in the amateur Muay Thai circuit.  
 
Christella wraps her hands in preparation for a sparring session leading up to the Ringmasters Finals at Madison Square Garden.
